snippet.title: Tower Of Madness: Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
❤️Wishlist the game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3177340/Tower_of_Madness/
Get ready to experience the Tower of Madness on October 25th! 

A narrative driven horror game where you play as John, a gunslinger, who stands alone as the sole survivor of his town and family. 

I made the game alone with bjorn and will be doing some game devlogs for the game in future.
